{"tid":1190070,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★二手續癲！藍田康田苑已補價賣778萬　創新高","createTime":"2019-06-07T06:30:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-08T07:43:48.000Z","uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"6025333137effb983ee577095226d841c89697b9","tid":1190070,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T06:30:56.000Z","msg":"世紀21聯誠謝寶昭表示，近日市場睇樓量及買賣偏靜，但繼續有破頂成交出現。藍田居屋康田苑A座中層2室，實用面積550方呎，上月底已補價自由市場開價798萬港元，終減至778萬元成交，仍創屋苑售價新高，呎價14,145元。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20190607/bkn-20190607141432926-0607_00842_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20190607%2Fbkn-20190607141432926-0607_00842_001.html&d=SmQqe2lJFulj5u2s5Cv8umVlCuV5KOpEhASsqV1EMe4%3D&h=00ecce4a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20190607/bkn-20190607141432926-0607_00842_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"78d3762664446764f270c1e0dd7e40b15647a557","tid":1190070,"uid":19454,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T06:31:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/4W0dlkv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F4W0dlkv.jpg&h=d772a520&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b1fcded10d07e67be1f16463d34a1fc13fa7993f","tid":1190070,"uid":19454,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T06:31:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SvLyiiS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSvLyiiS.jpg&h=a25883a0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cfccebf439998a9153f0dfa97d8d235ed06700e1","tid":1190070,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T06:32:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9yozuEE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9yozuEE.jpg&h=ce0c4453&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"241ae0fc92f2f530dc1f32a12560d3b7e867c418","tid":1190070,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":2,"